column5: Happy B-E-L-A-T-E-D sire....... Ya I missed it...sorry Bud...been super busy at school...its the first miss in near 6years....crikeky!!!!!!.  Anyway Bud...I hope your day was just awesome.  .so here'S to one of the finest: .....FIREFIGHTERS .....FATHERS .....HUSBANDS ....................MUSKY HUNTERS .....and someone I can rely on to tell me something straight...even if I dont like it ......You are a friend Lew...thanks Bud!  Betcha the wimmins gotcha something real decent.......
Happy birthday lew !!!!   ...i hope ya get all kinds of fishing goodies too !!!...cheers
Happy belated B'DAY Lew!!!....  We've got to get together next year here on the river for a bit of Muskie Huntin'  Hope ya had a super day!!!!
Happy belated birthday Mr. Happy!
Belated Happy Birthday Lew.....Sorry I missed it we are away in Florida for a week.
Happy 39th Birthday Lew  I hope you catch a 60 inch Muskie next year.  See ya in Lakair.  MTP
OOps, almost missed it. Hope it was a great birthday!  Pam
Hope yer days been swell Lew. Happt B-DAY to you SIR. This pepsi,s for you.
Happy birthday Lew, may the musky gods be kind to you once again this year!
All the best Lew!
Happy Day, Dude   .
Best Fishes, Lew.
All the very best to you Lew, keep em coming!
Happy Bday Lew hope ya had a good one.
Hey Lew .. Happy Birthday ... (albeit a little late in the day) ... hope it was a great day for ya.
Thank you  once again folks for all your B-Day wishes, there much appreciated !!

Opps I forgot to ask, is ther any cake left over?
Have a wonderful day Lew, what's left of it and happy birthday

Happy B-day Lew!
....Hope it was a great day Lew and may a great year follow.
lets make it a week long celebration  Happy birthday ( belated )  Dave
happy birthday Lew! Hope you have a great day!

Sounds good to me Dave....as long as the gifts keep coming for a week  Thanks again everyone !!
There was CAKE !!!  Nobody told me there was cake...  DANG ! I likes cake...
Happy B-day Lew. May you have many more. You still have thousands of muskies to catch. Have a good one.
